leadership-approach|results_process_vision_people|strength_1|1|Clear movement|When this pattern is working well, Results gives leadership a clear line of movement. Decisions, owners, and next steps are easier to see, so the work is less likely to sit in drift or unresolved discussion.|results|active|leadership-approach::results_process_vision_people::strength_1
leadership-approach|results_process_vision_people|strength_2|2|Progress with a working method|Results and Process together can turn intention into progress people can follow. The strength is not just moving quickly; it is making the outcome, route, and handover clear enough for others to carry.|process|active|leadership-approach::results_process_vision_people::strength_2
leadership-approach|results_process_vision_people|strength_3|3|Range through stronger trust after Vision|Vision can broaden the first two signals before People is brought in deliberately. People adds range when the pattern has movement, structure, or direction and now needs better communication around the human impact. It can make progress more sustainable because people understand their part in the work.|people|active|leadership-approach::results_process_vision_people::strength_3
leadership-approach|results_process_people_vision|strength_1|1|Clear movement|When this pattern is working well, Results gives leadership a clear line of movement. Decisions, owners, and next steps are easier to see, so the work is less likely to sit in drift or unresolved discussion.|results|active|leadership-approach::results_process_people_vision::strength_1
